<app-carousel [elements]="carouselElements"/>
<div class="mission">
  <h1 class="headingMission">Our Mission</h1>
  <p class="parMission">
    At YourScope, we know that every student has the potential to succeed, and we want to 
    do everything we can to make that happen. Our service provides students with a course 
    planner, an events tracker, and an internal job board for students looking to find work early! 
    We strive to make your high school experience as smooth and enjoyable as possible.
  </p>
</div>
