  <table>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <h2>Perfect For Students and Employers</h2>
        <br />
        <p>
          Our service provides employers with a platform to seek young and talented new workers, 
          giving students an opportunity to gain valuable life skills and workplace experience 
          before they even graduate high school. Employers can register a YourScope account 
          and can share job postings on the network, reaching many talented people looking for work. 
          With YourScope, searching for applicants has never been easier!
        </p>
      </td>
      <td>
        <img src="../../assets/landing/career.png">
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>
<br />
<div class="split" data-aos="zoom-in">
