        <img src="../../assets/landing/school.png" class="imgSchool">
      </td>
      <td>
        <h2 class="rightAlign">Partnering With Schools</h2>
        <p class="rightAlign">
          YourScope partners with schools all across Ontario in order to ensure accurate information 
          regarding offered courses and upcoming events are provided to students. When a school partners 
          with YourScope, an admin account will be created for them which can be used to monitor and 
          update offered courses and events.
      </td>
